e vigiar meu carro?

247
00:15:17,334 --> 00:15:19,044
Seu carro?

248
00:15:19,169 --> 00:15:20,921
É.

249
00:15:22,339 --> 00:15:23,841
Vamos.

250
00:15:27,928 --> 00:15:29,930
Espere aqui um instante.

251
00:15:37,855 --> 00:15:39,064
